name: Stay the fck home
description:
2021, gif, collage of an original watercolour painting and digital elements

"Stay the fck home": I bet you've heard this over and over again these past two years. Well, guess what? Rebel girl stayed home all alone. And this happened. The days started getting shorter, and the nights colder... What happened next is depicted on this image.
... Be careful what you see. 

If u collect it, you're protected.

XOXO,
JessyJeanne
